 century, when the picture became more fragmented."]}]},{"name":"ap","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Loving’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Gwilym ap Meurig was born about 1328, in Breconshire, Wales, United Kingdom, his father, Meurig \"Ddu\" ap Rhys, was 28 and his mother, Mrs. Meurig Ddu ap Rhys, was 24. He had at least 1 son with Mrs. Gwilym ap Meurig."},"et":{"about 1328–":"umbes 1328–Surnud","1328–Male":"1328–Surnud","1330–Male":"1330–Surnud","1332–Female":"1332–Surnud","1354–Male":"1354–Surnud","1302–Male":"1302–Surnud","1306–Female":"1306–Surnud","1302":"1302","about 1328":"umbes 1328","1354":"1354","1332":"1332","1330":"1330","about 1354":"umbes 1354","1306":"1306","1328":"1328","of Llangoed,Llys-wen,Breconshire,Wales":"Breconshire, Wales, United Kingdom","of,Cantref Selyf,Breconshire,Wales":"Cantref, Breconshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1328–":"noin 1328–Kuollut","1328–Male":"1328–Kuollut","1330–Male":"1330–Kuollut","1332–Female":"1332–Kuollut","1354–Male":"1354–Kuollut","1302–Male":"1302–Kuollut","1306–Female":"1306–Kuollut","1302":"1302","about 1328":"noin 1328","1354":"1354","1332":"1332","1330":"1330","about 1354":"noin 1354","1306":"1306","1328":"1328","of Llangoed,Llys-wen,Breconshire,Wales":"Breconshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","of,Cantref Selyf,Breconshire,Wales":"Cantref, Breconshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1328–":"environ 1328–Décédé","1328–Male":"1328–Décédé","1330–Male":"1330–Décédé","1332–Female":"1332–Décédée","1354–Male":"1354–Décédé","1302–Male":"1302–Décédé","1306–Female":"1306–Décédée","1302":"1302","about 1328":"environ 1328","1354":"1354","1332":"1332","1330":"1330","about 1354":"environ 1354","1306":"1306","1328":"1328","of Llangoed,Llys-wen,Breconshire,Wales":"Breconshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","of,Cantref Selyf,Breconshire,Wales":"Cantref, Breconshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","li